{
  "stem": "9728.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was the last time that I ever saw my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I left in January in 1940, when I went back to Lodz, this was it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never heard from them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never saw them, except one letter at a later date that I will mention I received from them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They closed the ghetto around April 1940.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They closed the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By closing the ghetto, they made-- they put the barbed wire around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In every, every two, three corners stood a German with a weapon.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we could not get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If you even came close by, they had a guy to shoot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they killed a lot of people that they wanted to get out, some of them at night, some of them at dusk, that they thought that they will be able to get out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The reas--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, where our building was was a-- a small block from our building was the, was the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did not see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not see this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I saw the blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw the blood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some-- there was one German soldier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He must have been a, a, a real terrible guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because what he did-- they had an order if you crossed the barbed wire, that they had a guy to shoot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But as long as you were inside of the ghetto, inside of the barbed wire, officially they had no right to shoot you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this fellow would call someone, a Jew, to come over, come over, come over here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So some people were afraid and they came near.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He told them to come over on the other side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If they were smart, they wouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
